body: "## Context\nThe bundled package catalog in docs/EXTENSIONS.md (around lines 220-227) mentions only pm-beads, pm-todos, pm-lifecycle-hooks, and pm-search-advanced as exemplars. pm-linked-test-adapters is shipped under packages/ but has zero presence in public docs.\n\ndocs/TESTING.md covers pm test / pm test-all / background runs but never mentions that pm install linked-test-adapters --project unlocks run management adapters and reporters.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- docs/EXTENSIONS.md bundled-package exemplar table/list is complete: all packages/pm-* appear\n- docs/TESTING.md mentions pm-linked-test-adapters and what it adds\n- pm install linked-test-adapters --project example exists in TESTING.md\n\n## Evidence\npackages/pm-linked-test-adapters/package.json (name, description); docs/EXTENSIONS.md lines 220-227; docs/TESTING.md full file — no mention"
